I"R<h1 id="spaghetti-carbonara">Spaghetti Carbonara</h1>

<p>Let’s see how to cook your chosen dish.</p>

<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<p>Here is what you need to have at home.</p>

<ol>
  <li>250g, spaghetti,</li>
  <li>2, fresh eggs,</li>
  <li>150ml, single cream,</li>
  <li>100g, parmesan cheese,</li>
  <li>100g, lardons,</li>
  <li>Seasoning: black pepper only.</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="preparation">Preparation</h2>

<p>Time: Takes as long as it takes.<br />
Serves: Make sure to share, and buy for your pals.</p>

<p>Here are the steps to cook the meal. Enjoy!</p>

<ol>
  <li>Start playing music in the background.</li>
  <li>Pore a glass of drink for the chef.</li>
  <li>Fry the lardons in a pan.</li>
  <li>Beat the eggs and add the cream to it.</li>
  <li>Sprinkle the cheese into the fluid and whisk it.</li>
  <li>Season with lots of black pepper.</li>
  <li>Cook the spaghetti, and as soon as it’s done, add it to the sauce while it’s hot, such that the eggs can cook a little and the cheese can melt.</li>
  <li>Mix and add the fried lardons.</li>
  <li>Serve and enjoy.</li>
</ol>

